  <h2 id="if-youre-using-linux--mac--unix">If youâ€™re using Linux / Mac / Unix</h2>

  <p>$ ssh login_name@###.###.###.###</p>

  <p>or (if you have more than one private key)</p>

  <p>$ ssh â€“i ~/.ssh/My_Key_Pair.pem login_name@###.###.###.###</p>
